# Raw ai-observe artifacts are large and SENSITIVE (contain absolute paths,
# wrapped-command argv/prompts, and raw syscall text -- see repo README's
# sensitive-data warning). Never commit them. Curated *_report.json /
# *_summary.json derivations (relative paths, no raw_syscall) are committed.
**/data/output/*.trace
**/data/output/*.jsonl
**/data/output/*.jsonl.partial
**/data/output/*.jsonl.rebuilt
**/data/output/*.meta.json

# Scratch working dirs the driven agents write into.
**/work/
**/_smoke_work/
